snippet.textDisplay: Since last season, Coke Studio Pakistan is clearly more focused on creating diversified videos rather than deliberating on the quality of music itself. For me the contemporary adolescent lyrics, ordinary yet modern gadget based compositions and rapping are getting way more space. Management needs to consider the interest of old school music lovers as well.
